<p><q>A man of the fifteenth century, inheriting its strange web of
belief and unbelief, of epicurean levity and <qex>fetichistic</qex>
dread.</q> <rj><qau>G. Eliot.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

